						<span class="authorlink"><a href='http://trilema.com/2014/the-psychology-of-the-bagholder?b=Contrary%20to%20&amp;e=ier.#select' class='url'>The psychology of the bagholder on Trilema - A blog by Mircea Popescu.</a></span>&nbsp;(via Pingback)						<span class=""></span>
